title: Icons of the Sixties Bob Dylan & others
description:
Icons of the sixties

This 4 cd set gives some nice examples of the interaction between Bob Dylan and 
other great artists who have their roots in the sixties of the 20-th century. 
Thisset gives yous of course only a small example of how they did perform together 
at several occasions or plays each other music. Hope you like it.
A DylanNL production (www.dylannl.blogspot.com). Artwork Noirdesir France...
